      <li><a href="/reading/the-natural-framework-lean/removal/">Removal.lean</a> &mdash; removes each postcondition and shows the system dies, citing these axioms</li>
      <li><a href="/reading/the-natural-framework-lean/stochasticity/">Stochasticity.lean</a> &mdash; uses capacity_bound + BoundedTransducer to show deterministic limits</li>
      <li><a href="/reading/the-natural-framework-lean/pigeonhole/">Pigeonhole.lean</a> &mdash; the collision that capacity_bound enables</li>
    </ul>
